snippet.textDisplay:
theories:
• nick struggles to run the studio and gets emily to co-run with him, then ~possibly~ a relationship starts
• skip to 0:16, u notice that ozzy and kingston are the only characters on screen to share a white wall with lily, my theory is that she gets in between their bromance, probably kingston and lily falling in love as alluded in the off season ep
* richelle vs summer for dance captain, richelle gets it and other opportunities over her as she is the ‘face of absolute dance’ so summer pulls an ~amy from S6~ and leaves for dance mania
* love triangle between finn, amy and piper blah blah blah, id say piper keeps pushing finn away until finn gets sick of it and goes to amy
* jude might not be part of that leaked a-troupe line but i think at some point jude and cleo will be on the same team which is how they start to develop feelings for each other, or they could both even be the alternates for nationals and they bond over that???
* ozzy’s line ‘every dance battle i’ve ever fought’ might be alluding to his audition for male soloist??
* emily’s line ‘this could be the last time you do’ might take place just as tns takes the stage for the finals of nationals, where she reflects how she couldn’t dance with the team anymore bc of her knee, so she tells them that this could be the last time they dance together

thanks for listening to my ted talk

snippet.textDisplay:
I feel like Finn and piper are the most well thought out ship in this entire show. Even though piper wasn’t ready for a relationship during season 6, finn was always still there for her no matter what; in an alternate reality, when piper messed up her aerial, when she got really nervous, when she didn’t want to dance at prom, when she was scared about the duet, when miss Angela insulted her at the convention. But maybe that’s the thing. Maybe Finn always felt that he gave more than he got back from piper. I hope they fine a way back to each other tho bcos pinn are such a healthy pairing and they deserve each other. 
As for Amy, I’m gonna quote my lil brother here snd say she should go back to the cinemas with ty and eat some popcorn 😂 I really do love Amy as a character and I feel bad that she’s been through so many romances that haven’t worked out, but really? Your best friends guy? Maybe she didn’t know that piper likes Finn, but still. PINN ALL THE WAY, COMMENT OR LIKE IF YALL AGREE, THANKS FOR LISTENING TO MY RANT 😅😂💛
